        How to Prepare for Open Home Day as a Seller in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        The specific things sellers should do the morning of an open home, the week before, and after each inspection to build buyer momentum.
      </p>
